graphql.query:
query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	commonGetAttachmentLibraries (query: $query)
	{
		id
		filename
		mimetype
		extension
		relativePathSegments
		width
		height
		size
		url
		isCropable
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

		isCropable

}

}
